    <item>
      <title>联邦机构解雇员工，称其为错误，再次解雇他们</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-sba-tells-staff-it-didn-t-mean-to-fire-them-then-fires-them-the-next-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的小企业管理局告诉试用期员工，它错误地向他们发送了解雇通知，并于第二天通知其中一些人，他们毕竟被解雇了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-sba-tells-staff-it-didn-t-mean-to-fire-them-then-fires-them-the-next-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 04:04:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称俄罗斯在贝森特访问前向基辅发射导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/ukraine-says-russia-hit-kyiv-with-missiles-before-bessent-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰称，俄罗斯向基辅发射了弹道导弹。此举正值美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特准备访问乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基，以表明美国为结束战争所做出的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/ukraine-says-russia-hit-kyiv-with-missiles-before-bessent-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 03:38:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>若上诉失败，马来西亚必须为蒙古人死亡赔偿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/malaysia-must-pay-damages-for-mongolian-s-death-if-appeal-fails</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚一家法院命令该国政府立即向一名被谋杀的蒙古妇女的家人赔偿损失，只要该国推翻该裁决的上诉不成功。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/malaysia-must-pay-damages-for-mongolian-s-death-if-appeal-fails</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 03:32:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普提名两人出任美国财政部高级职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-nominates-two-people-for-top-posts-at-the-us-treasury</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博新闻周二晚间审阅的白宫向美国参议院发送的一份文件，唐纳德·特朗普总统已提名两人担任财政部高级职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-nominates-two-people-for-top-posts-at-the-us-treasury</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 03:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划任命 Quintenz 为美国衍生品监管机构负责人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-plans-to-pick-quintenz-as-head-of-us-derivatives-regulator</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据白宫发送给国会山的一份文件（彭博新闻社审阅了该文件），唐纳德·特朗普总统计划选择安德森·霍洛维茨旗下 a16z 加密货币部门的政策主管布莱恩·昆滕兹 (Brian Quintenz) 领导商品期货交易委员会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/trump-plans-to-pick-quintenz-as-head-of-us-derivatives-regulator</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 02:21:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯在菲律宾中期选举演讲中抨击中国和杜特尔特</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/marcos-slams-china-duterte-in-philippine-midterm-election-pitch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯在开始为其参议员候选人竞选时大力抨击中国，使得与北京的海上争端成为五月至关重要的中期选举的核心议题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/marcos-slams-china-duterte-in-philippine-midterm-election-pitch</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 02:18:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜抨击特朗普接管加沙计划的“篡位者”美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/north-korea-slams-usurper-us-over-trump-s-gaza-takeover-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜国家媒体谴责唐纳德·特朗普接管满目疮痍的加沙地带并控制格陵兰岛和巴拿马运河等其他领土的提议是侵略行为，称美国为一己私利侵犯其他国家权利的“篡位者”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/north-korea-slams-usurper-us-over-trump-s-gaza-takeover-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 01:08:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普欢迎俄罗斯释放美国公民 准备制定和平计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/russia-releases-american-teacher-as-trump-readies-peace-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普对俄罗斯释放一名被拘留的美国人表示欢迎，并表示希望此举将使两国能够共同努力结束乌克兰战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/russia-releases-american-teacher-as-trump-readies-peace-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 18:42:56 GMT</pubDate>
